  <p>If you have simple, routine questions: We have condensed our 40+ years of disc-stack centrifuge experience into <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-faq/">101 Frequently Asked Questions about Disc Stack Centrifuges</a>!</p>

  <h2 id="centrifuges-for-cider-or-juice-clarification-63f782c1-34bf-4217-adeb-40b68078f1b4">Centrifuges for Cider or Juice Clarification</h2>

  <p>Alfa Laval food-grade disc centrifuge is best suited for cider processing. High separation efficiency can be attained due to the very high g-force exerted by the centrifuge. Also, with mechanical separation, there is no need for manual filter changes, which leads to major cost savings on labor and filter media.</p>

